lead_paragraph: Detroit Tigers ace Justin Verlander and slugger Miguel Cabrera could be available for the right price. The Chicago White Sox might be prepared to deal Chris Sale, too.

headline.print_headline: Verlander, Cabrera, Sale Could Be Available on Trade Market
